13 years of waiting and after their first child , Comedian AY Makun and wife Mabel welcome their second child, a baby girl.
The comedian took to his Instagram page to share the good news. He revealed that their new bundle of joy has been named Ayomide.
”Our prayers in the last 13 years has been answered. AYOMIDE thank you for making @realmabelmakun and I, Mummy and Daddy again. Thank you for making Michelle a BIG SISTER. Thanks to everyone who kept us in their prayers and never stopped feeding us with positive vibes.
“ Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding; in all your ways submit to him, and he will make your paths straight.”
GOD’S TIME IS ALWAYS THE BEST”he wrote.
AY and Mabel already have a daughter, Michelle.
